I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away.
I was watching the new NewsBreak training by xevio, and I saw that users can get up to $25,000 ad credit. What are the conditions?

To redeem an ad credit on NewsBreak, you need to create an account and choose the Prepay billing option. Ad credits are a promotional form of payment for ads. For more detailed information on how to redeem your ad credit, you can check out this guide: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17391456255629-How-to-redeem-a-NewsBreak-ad-credit). If you have any other questions, feel free to ask!
